################################################################################
# Lernfunk-Admin-UI                                                            #
################################################################################
# The Admin-UI is part of the lernfunk-project, an open source content         #
# mangement system for educational audio-visual content.                       #
#                                                                              #
# This is the admin interface for adding, updating and deleting content        #
# (mediaobjects, feeds, series, ...)                                           #
#                                                                              #
# You can find more information about the lernfunk project at:                 #
#  - http://code.google.com/p/lernfunk/                                        #
#  - http://www.lernfunk.de/                                                   #
#                                                                              #
# If you are interested in virtUOS check out our website                       #
#   http://www.virtuos.uni-osnabrueck.de                                       #
#                                                                              #
# This software is free software under GPL 3.                                  #
#                                                                              #
################################################################################
# How to build/deploy the admin-ui                                             #
################################################################################
# On Unix/Linux:                                                               #
#                                                                              #
# 1. Run  ./make_release_build.sh  A folder "release" is created, containing   #
#    the ready to work admin-ui.                                               #
# 2. Change directory to "release/php"                                         #
# 3. Edit "config.php" (Most important is the correct path to the Lernfunk-    #
#    baselib                                                                   #
# 4. Copy the contens of release to a webserver                                #
#                                                                              #
#                                                                              #
# On Windows:                                                                  #
#                                                                              #
# 1. Istall Python for Windows:                                                #
#    http://www.python.org/download/releases/2.7.3/                            #
# 2. Install Git for Windows:                                                  #
#    http://tinyurl.com/cuzmbn2                                                #
#    You might also want to install a graphical user interface for git:        #
#    http://code.google.com/p/tortoisegit/downloads/list                       #
# 3. Check out lernfunk and go to                                              #
#    lernfunk/admin-ui/admin-interface                                         #
# 4. Run make_release_build.py. A folder "release" is created, containing      #
#    the ready to work admin-ui.                                               #
# 5. Go to release/php.                                                        #
# 6. Edit "config.php" (Most important is the correct path to the Lernfunk-    #
#    baselib                                                                   #
# 7. Copy the contens of release to a webserver                                #
#                                                                              #
################################################################################
